# Remoulade Sauce

> A zesty and creamy condiment perfect for seafood, sandwiches, or grilled meats. This version has a Cajun-inspired twist with horseradish, chives, and smoked paprika. #sauce #condiment #cajun #seafood

- Mayonnaise | 2/3 cup | 
- Garlic | 2 cloves | 
- Chives | 2 tsp | 
- Mustard | Dijon, 1 tbsp | 
- Lemon | 1 tbsp | Juiced
- Worcestershire Sauce | 1 tsp | 
- Lemon | 1 tsp | Zested
- Horseradish | 1 1/2 tsp | 
- Cayenne Pepper | 1 pinch | 
- Smoked Paprika | 3/4 tsp | 
- Salt | 1/4 tsp | 

In a bowl, combine all ingredients and stir until well incorporated. Chill for at least 30 minutes before serving to allow flavors to meld.
